	<h2>Our Commitment</h2>
	<p>A big difference between travel providers who are after the LGBT market and OffTo.com is our connection to the community we serve. OffTo.com was created by openly LGBT professionals and allies. We are committed to providing the kind of unparalleled service that offers something for every member of the LGBT community. OffTo’s commitment extends far beyond travel interests into the daily lives of LGBT individuals – we are committed to supporting LGBT community organizations, non-profits, events and entrepreneurs.</p>
	
